{"tid":846291,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"普巴鼓勵隊友：繼續為曼聯奮戰！","createTime":"2018-10-03T10:17:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T17:31:38.000Z","uid":16659,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e7a4d5519b37621d67ff8bd9a227051e41e693c9","tid":846291,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T10:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/0/270/23086849270/23089321341_600x391.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F0%2F270%2F23086849270%2F23089321341_600x391.JPG&h=55526533&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=%2BX40yYmwoEG9YEvn5HZpUYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=804b7ab9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯中場保羅普巴賽後在Twitter激勵隊友繼續努力加油，儼然球隊的領袖。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯周二歐聯分組賽主場與華倫西亞互交白卷，球員的表現再次備受抨擊。不過貴為主將之一，近期新聞人物保羅普巴（Paul Pogba）在比賽期間及賽後俱顯得具戰意，他賽後在社交網站寫道：「繼續為曼聯奮戰！」，這個留言短短幾小時已經有接近2萬個「like」，支持者之中，有人留言要領隊摩連奴滾蛋。<br />\n<br />\n普巴今仗未能帶領球隊贏波，但場上一個片段卻令他贏得不少掌聲，他一次在中場迎波後，看到難以把皮波傳向前場，於是用手勢要中鋒盧卡古多跑動，或回來主動迎接傳球。這個做法贏得網民支持，表示終於有人看到盧卡古在偷懶。<br />\n<br />\n不過也有網友發現普巴自己也有失誤，一次對方在右路突破，普巴上前正要防守竟然倒地摸起左腳腕，結果對手在無人看管直奔底線傳中。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : Twitter圖片"},{"pid":"e6a55fb16e21b2a08838c26e224d045cd31b1f94","tid":846291,"uid":16659,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T10:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://media.giphy.com/media/9DcxwUK4C4seesf9d0/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F9DcxwUK4C4seesf9d0%2Fgiphy.gif&h=04c8042f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHere to help=Pogba<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40114132e240ab22a3149a78c72b8f91f709a410","tid":846291,"ui